{"id":60671,"date":"2024-11-15T19:12:17","date_gmt":"2024-11-15T13:42:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=60671"},"modified":"2024-11-15T19:12:22","modified_gmt":"2024-11-15T13:42:22","slug":"hinged-wardrobe-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/hinged-wardrobe-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Hinged Wardrobe Designs That are Designer-Approved!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Hinged wardrobe designs\u2014For those who want storage with a side of sophistication, open up to a world of style!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you have a small, cosy closet or a spacious walk-in, hinged wardrobe doors give you that simple elegance and ease that makes your every day feel less chaotic. No more misaligned tracks or jammed doors! These classic beauties have been around forever but have evolved and stayed on-trend every season.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you are ready for cupboard doors that do the job and look good, keep reading. We have the full scoop on how to incorporate hinged wardrobe designs and make your space stylish. Read on!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What are Hinge Wardrobes?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hinge wardrobes feature doors attached to a frame using hinges, which allows them to open outwards in a full swing. We have all seen these classic cupboards first in our grandparents&#8217; homes. These styles have simple door mechanisms, are reliable, and are efficient.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hinge wardrobe designs offer flexibility in terms of style, size, and function. Whether you have a small bedroom or a spacious <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/walk-in-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">walk-in closet<\/a>, they can be customised to fit your needs. You can have single or double doors, which can be made from various materials like wood, glass, or even metal\u2014whatever suits your style best. The doors open wide, giving you full access to the contents, so you can quickly find your favourite outfit without hassle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190854\/what-are-hinge-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"What are hinge wardrobe\" class=\"wp-image-60677\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190854\/what-are-hinge-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190854\/what-are-hinge-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190854\/what-are-hinge-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190854\/what-are-hinge-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Crafted to open up to all your essentials in one go<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your Go-To Guide for Stylish Hinge Wardrobe Designs\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to add some flair to your wardrobe game? Here\u2019s our exciting style guide on hinge wardrobe designs. From smooth-as-butter door swings to stylish finishes that make a statement, these designs are perfect for those who love a classic vibe with a twist! Check it out.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Prim up in Style: Hinged Mirrored Wardrobe Door With a Pullout\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This hinge wardrobe has got it all: style, storage, and a sleek mirror pull-out. It\u2019s not just a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobe design<\/a> but an entire dressing room right in your bedroom. Just forget squeezing in a dressing table or makeup essentials falling everywhere. This design combines it all in one sleek unit. Swing open the doors, pull out the mirror unit and voila, a hidden section of the shelf will come out holding your favourite perfumes and daily makeup essentials.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Say goodbye to clutter and hello to chic, streamlined mornings\u2014your new Hinged Mirrored Wardrobe Door design style has your back! Just slide the mirror out and dive into your organised stash. Running late? Grab what you need in seconds without the endless drawer shuffle. It\u2019s a genius space-saver for small rooms and an absolute style statement for any space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190804\/hinged-mirrored-wardrobe-doors.jpg\" alt=\"Hinged mirrored wardrobe door with sleek design, hidden storage, and pull-out mirror for organised mornings\" class=\"wp-image-60672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190804\/hinged-mirrored-wardrobe-doors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190804\/hinged-mirrored-wardrobe-doors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190804\/hinged-mirrored-wardrobe-doors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190804\/hinged-mirrored-wardrobe-doors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Style check and storage solution made simple<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Class Meets Glass: Stunning Modern Hinged Wardrobe Doors\u00a0\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern hinged wardrobe design with a glass door turns your storage game from functional to fabulous. With trendy glass doors, you can admire your sartorial collection in a blink. Talk about a wardrobe that practically shows off for you! But this isn&#8217;t just about looks. Behind those crystal-clear glass doors lies an organisational masterpiece. Every inch of space is carefully crafted to maximise storage, with shelves and compartments that make it easy to store everything from jackets to shoes.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Need quick access to your essentials? A glance through the glass, and you can instantly spot that favourite jacket or handbag\u2014no more digging through piles. With dedicated compartments for accessories, shoes, and all your essentials, it&#8217;s a compact powerhouse of storage solutions that doesn\u2019t compromise on style.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190834\/modern-hinged-wardrobe-doors.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek modern hinged wardrobe with glass doors offers stylish storage for clothing and accessories\" class=\"wp-image-60675\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190834\/modern-hinged-wardrobe-doors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190834\/modern-hinged-wardrobe-doors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190834\/modern-hinged-wardrobe-doors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190834\/modern-hinged-wardrobe-doors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A cupboard that flaunts your fashion, even when it\u2019s closed!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Soft Close Wardrobe Door Hinge Design With Ample Storage\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Style and practicality make this soft-close wardrobe door hinge design a masterpiece. Combining refreshing mint green and soft blush pink creates a soothing but stylish look. Every section of this space is thoughtfully designed to hold everything from books, blankets, bags, and clothes. You can see a smart mix of closed doors and open sections. Also, overhead storage can store seasonal items without hassle.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This hinge wardrobe design tastefully incorporates a little window seat, letting natural light flood in without obstructing the view. You can curl up with a good book and a cup of piping hot coffee or unwind and gaze outside.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190843\/soft-close-wardrobe-door-hinges.jpg\" alt=\"Soft close wardrobe door hinge in mint green and blush pink, enhancing style and practicality in storage\" class=\"wp-image-60676\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190843\/soft-close-wardrobe-door-hinges.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190843\/soft-close-wardrobe-door-hinges-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190843\/soft-close-wardrobe-door-hinges-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190843\/soft-close-wardrobe-door-hinges-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">All in one dream space!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Maximise Functionality: Hinge Wardrobe Design With a TV Unit\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Who says wardrobes can only hold clothes or other everyday essentials? This hinged wardrobe door design with a built-in TV unit nails it! There&#8217;s no need for cluttered corners with a separate <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-stand-design-ideas\/\">TV stand<\/a> or to lose precious storage space. It\u2019s perfect for compact spaces or those wanting to get the most out of their room. The TV is right before you while you are getting ready and enjoying your favourite show simultaneously. Isn\u2019t this a clever combo to incorporate into your home decor without compromising storage and space?\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190824\/hinge-wardrobe-with-tv-unit.jpg\" alt=\"Hinge wardrobe with built-in TV unit for sleek storage and entertainment in compact spaces\" class=\"wp-image-60674\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190824\/hinge-wardrobe-with-tv-unit.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190824\/hinge-wardrobe-with-tv-unit-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190824\/hinge-wardrobe-with-tv-unit-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/15190824\/hinge-wardrobe-with-tv-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Double the function, double the fun!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These hinge wardrobe designs add the wow factor to your home interiors. From smooth, effortless swings to custom finishes that show off your style, these designs give you everything you need and more. Let your wardrobe swing open to a world of style and make your closet the best part of your room. Ready to level up your storage game? Talk to the experts at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> for more.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs on Hinged Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1. How to choose a hinged wardrobe design?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the perfect hinged wardrobe design is all about balancing space, style, and functionality. Start with your room layout\u2014hinged doors need space to open fully, so ensure enough clearance in front of the cupboard is available, especially if your room is compact. If you are tight on space, opt for single doors or a minimalistic design to keep things sleek.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, think about style. These designs come in various materials and finishes, from classic wood and laminate to mirrored or glass doors. Consider your storage needs. Do you need more hanging space, drawers, or shelves? Hinged wardrobes offer flexibility in interior layouts, so you can customise compartments, add drawers, or even install pull-out racks for shoes and accessories.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2. What are the advantages of a hinged-door wardrobe?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When the doors open fully, you can see and reach everything inside without obstructions. This makes organising and finding items quicker, especially if you have many pieces.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hinged wardrobes come in a range of styles and finishes, allowing you to match them to your room\u2019s aesthetic. They also work well with added elements like mirrors or decorative handles, letting you personalise the look. These are highly customisable. They can be tailored with shelves, hanging rods, and drawers to fit your storage needs. Whether your space is large or compact, hinged wardrobes can adapt, making them a versatile and timeless choice for any bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3. How are hinged wardrobe doors different from other types of wardrobe doors?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hinged wardrobe doors stand out for their traditional swing-open design, which offers complete access to the cupboard\u2019s interior. Unlike sliding doors, which move side-to-side on a track and only open half the cupboard at a time, hinged doors open outward, letting you see and reach all sections easily.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another difference is in design versatility. Hinged doors can fit a variety of styles\u2014from classic wood panels to sleek mirrored finishes\u2014and can include unique handles and knobs, giving you more ways to customise. They are also suitable for large and compact spaces, though they need some clearance to open fully.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4. How can you choose the right size hinged wardrobe doors for your wardrobe?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To choose the right size for hinged wardrobe doors, start by measuring the height and width of your wardrobe opening. Standard hinged doors usually work best when there is enough space in front for the doors to swing fully open. If you have a compact room, consider choosing narrower doors to save space and avoid crowding.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, consider the number of doors. Larger wardrobes can have multiple narrower doors instead of one large door, making them easier to open and close. Finally, check that the door height complements your cupboard\u2019s design and room layout\u2014taller doors can add a sense of height and elegance, while shorter doors keep things compact.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" 